I"9<h2>Cannot get Remmina to copy and paste from client to server?</h2>

<p>Here is the solution:</p>

<p>1) Open Terminal and paste the following code</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>sudo apt-add-repository ppa:remmina-ppa-team/remmina-next

sudo apt-get update

sudo apt-get install remmina remmina-plugin-rdp
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>2) Now close Remmina RDP Client and open it again.</p>

